(528,1,'2017-01-20 16:00:20','2017-01-20 13:00:20','Royal Associates Insurance Brokers is one of East Africaâs fastest growing insurance broking firms with the clout and connections of a big player. We offer tailored insurance risk solutions that meet our clientsâ unique needs and are aligned to industry best practice.\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Design an innovative programme to suit the individual client</li>\r\n<li>We ensure the terms are realistically broad</li>\r\n<li>Negotiate competitive prices despite the broad terms of cover</li>\r\n<li>The policies are placed with insurance companies of repute, with sound financial security and positive attitude towards claims</li>\r\n<li>Ensure all claims are negotiated and expeditiously settled</li>\r\n<li>We keep clients appraised of changes taking place in the insurance world on a regular basis</li>\r\n<li>We conduct a risk survey and implement a risk management programme.  This can ultimately assist to substantially reduce insurance costs/</li>\r\n<li>We offer insurance and risk related training to clients</li>\r\n<li>There are mandatory monthly claims review meetings</li>\r\n<li>Quarterly underwriting and risk review meetings.  If there is need to hold other meetings outside such structured schedules this will definitely take place.</li>\r\n<li>To ensure that we are keeping up to the standards, we execute a service level agreement that we love to follow religiously.</li>\r\n<ul>\r\n\r\n','About Us','Royal Associates Insurance Brokers is one of East Africaâs fastest growing insurance broking firms with the clout and connections of a big player. We offer tailored insurance risk solutions that meet our clientsâ unique needs and are aligned to industry best practice.','inherit','closed','closed','','103-revision-v1','','','2017-01-20 16:00:20','2017-01-20 13:00:20','',103,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/blog/103-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
