(580,1,'2017-01-25 16:33:14','2017-01-25 13:33:14','At Royal Associates Insurance, we have a pool of professionals experienced in structuring various policies to cater for various clientsâ specific requirements. We do reviews on a regular basis to take advantage of developments in the insurance market as they occur.\r\n\r\nWe make appropriate improvements in the scope of cover in order to make our policies cost effective and dispute free in the event of a claim. \r\nThese includes:\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Restructuring the policies,\r\n<li>Including all the relevant extensive clauses</li>\r\n<li>Reviewing the premium rating structure</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n \r\nWe ensure that the warranties applying under each of the policies do not unreasonably prejudice your protection.\r\n','Property Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','property-insurance','','','2017-05-15 21:41:18','2017-05-15 18:41:18','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=580',0,'product','',0),
(581,1,'2017-01-25 14:32:14','2017-01-25 11:32:14','Legal suits as a result of work places injuries are also becoming a phenomenon. Compensation of injured employees under the WIBA does not prevent them from pursuing a further claim legally under the common law. These type of suits can be a nuisance and very expensive to defend!\r\nAt Royal Associates Insurance, we offer an adequate solution in form of Employers liability cover and your only requirement is to forward all the demand letters and court summons un answered for the insuresâ appointed legal experts to defend on your behalf.\r\n','Employers Liability Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','employers-liability-insurance','','','2017-02-03 11:55:18','2017-02-03 08:55:18','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=581',0,'product','',0),
