(587,1,'2017-01-25 22:59:20','2017-01-25 19:59:20','Burglaries or theft at commercial premises are on increase and the importance of an adequate cover cannot be over emphasised. Burglary cover falls under our property insurance line and as mentioned in the opening section, we will use our expertise to structure an ideal policy to cover your specific requirements.\r\n\r\nWe will negotiate for the right rating structure with a factor on an ideal first loss level de4pending on the level of exposure.\r\n\r\nWe will review the policy to ensure that the warranties and restrictions do not unnecessarily prejudice your protection.\r\n','Burglary','','publish','closed','closed','','burglary','','','2017-01-25 22:59:20','2017-01-25 19:59:20','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=587',0,'product','',0),
