(589,1,'2017-01-25 23:27:24','2017-01-25 20:27:24','As the name suggests, all risks policy provides cover against all risks not specifically excluded.\r\n\r\nOur professionals will arrange for an ideal cover at the most appropriate coste. We will scrutinise the warranties and restrictions to ensure that your protection is not unnecessary prejudiced. The cover will carry all the necessary extensive clauses to ensure that there is no gap in coverage. \r\n\r\n Since this policy excludes loss or damage following electrical or mechanical derangement, we highly recommend an isolation of all electronic equipment items to be covered under an appropriate Electronic equipment policy. \r\n','All Risk Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','all-risk-insurance','','','2017-01-25 23:27:24','2017-01-25 20:27:24','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=589',0,'product','',0),
