(593,1,'2017-01-26 00:11:15','2017-01-25 21:11:15','For large Industrial operators with machinery and equipments highly susceptible to breakdown, it will be ideal to take an Industrial All Risks cover in place of the traditional Fire and perils and fire Business interruption and, burglary. This is an insurance package which mainly incorporates Fire & Allied Perils, Burglary, Accidental damage and Business Interruption and it provides indemnity to the property insured against any loss or damage from any cause not excluded by the policy\r\n\r\nHowever, the policy carries higher deductibles and therefore one needs to strike a balance before settling on the ideal cover.\r\n\r\nAt Royal Associates Insurance Brokers , our experienced team of professionals will guide you appropriately on the ideal cover depending on the prevailing circumstances and the exposures.\r\n','Industrial All Risk','','publish','closed','closed','','industrial-all-risk','','','2017-02-06 08:24:17','2017-02-06 05:24:17','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=593',0,'product','',0),
(597,1,'2017-01-26 01:12:44','2017-01-25 22:12:44','The policy provides indemnity to the insured against loss and/or destruction/damage to glass including louvre venting, partitions and roof lights by accident or misfortune of a accidental nature.  There are options either to replace the broken glass according to description or to pay the sum equivalent to the value of the broken glass at the time of loss, destruction or breakage up to the insurance value.  Cover can be arranged for cabinet glass, display signs, fixed glass and glass partitions on premises.','Plate Glass Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','plate-glass-insurance','','','2017-01-26 01:12:44','2017-01-25 22:12:44','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=597',0,'product','',0),
(598,1,'2017-01-26 00:57:23','2017-01-25 21:57:23','Indemnity/cover against loss of money and damage to safe or strong room damaged in the course of theft of money\r\nDefinition of Money:\r\nCash, bank notes, current postage and revenue stamps, gift vouchers, travellers cheques, foreign currency equivalent and any documents or instruments exchangeable for cash or goods at their face value.\r\n\r\nThis policy covers loss or damage to money by robbery or theft whilst: \r\n<ol>\r\n<li>In transit from your premises to the bank and vice versa</li> \r\n<li>In your premises during business hours</li> \r\n<li>In your premises in locked safes/strong rooms outside business hours</li> \r\n<li>In the hand of senior employees/authorised personnel of the company</li>\r\n<li>NHIF and service charge stamps and stamped cards and the contents of the franking machine</li>\r\n<li>Damage to safes and /or strong rooms</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n','Money Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','money-insurance','','','2017-01-26 00:57:23','2017-01-25 21:57:23','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=598',0,'product','',0),
