(603,1,'2017-01-26 01:43:36','2017-01-25 22:43:36','Machinery Breakdown Insurance Indemnity against any unforeseen physical loss of or damage to the specified plant as a result of any cause not excluded by the policy.\r\n \r\nThe purpose of machinery insurance is: \r\n<ul>\r\n<li>To cover the cost of repairing or replacing breakdown or losses to machinery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n','Machinery Breakdown Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','machinery-breakdown-insurance','','','2017-02-10 20:07:09','2017-02-10 17:07:09','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=603',0,'product','',0),
