(620,1,'2017-01-26 09:03:24','2017-01-26 06:03:24','Indemnity against direct pecuniary loss resulting from fraud or dishonesty of employees. Fidelity guarantee may be bought by any organization or person who may suffer as the result of the dishonesty, failure in the loyal performance of duty or, in certain cases, the mistake of another. \r\n\r\nThe policy covers the employer against loss of money and/or stock through dishonest acts of employees.\r\n\r\nPERSONS COVERED: All employees of the Insured who handle money, stocks, stores and accounting documents\r\n','Fidelity Guarantee','','publish','closed','closed','','fidelity-guarantee','','','2017-01-26 09:03:24','2017-01-26 06:03:24','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=620',0,'product','',0),
