(625,1,'2017-01-26 09:48:00','2017-01-26 06:48:00','Every day we are experiencing accidents in our business environment that injure, hurt or even kill third parties around us. Third party properties could also be destroyed by our business activities.\r\n\r\nOur Public/ product liability cover provides indemnity against legal liability to third parties in respect of accidental death, bodily injury and / or illness and / or loss of or damage to property incurred in the course of the Insuredâs business.\r\n','Public + Products Liability','','publish','closed','closed','','public-products-liability','','','2017-02-03 00:41:58','2017-02-02 21:41:58','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=625',0,'product','',0),
(626,1,'2017-01-26 09:54:09','2017-01-26 06:54:09','Banks and other financial institutions face a higher level of exposure to financial loss resulting from criminal behaviour than most other institutions.  Employee theft, embezzlement, forgery, hold up and fraud are all real risks in today\'s business environment and even more so in the financial sector.  \r\n\r\nComprehensive Bankers Blanket Bond provides comprehensive cover for crime and Fidelity package designed specifically for banks and other Financial Institutions. \r\n','Bankers Comprehensive Crime Insurance','','publish','closed','closed','','bankers-comprehensive-crime-insurance','','','2017-01-26 09:54:09','2017-01-26 06:54:09','',0,'http://royalassociates.co.ke/?post_type=product&#038;p=626',0,'product','',0),
